" Disabled meta combinations

" Duplicate keys
"map ¬± <D-¬¨>

" Dead keys (for doing accents)
"map ` <D-\>
"map ¬¥ <D-e>
"map ÀÜ <D-i>
"map Àú <D-n>
"map ¬® <D-u>

" Useful ones to keep
"map ‚Ä¢ <D-8>
"map ‚Äì <D-->
"map ‚Äî <D-_>
"map ‚Äô <D-6>
"map ‚Äú <D-[>
"map ‚Äò <D-]>
"map ‚Äù <D-{>
"map ‚Äô <D-}>

